description:
Save the date! 🗓️

SymPOWEsium 2025 is happening February 1st from 9am-5pm 💖

Get excited for a day of amazing events, learning, and empowering the women in engineering community 🦸‍♀️. It’s a day you won’t want to miss! 🌟 

‼️Open to mcgill and other Montreal women and gender minority students 

🔗 Link in bio for the interest form 

➡️ The interest form will keep you updated with emails when early registration and more information is available

Celebrate the end of the semester and the holidays with POWE at our White Elephant gift exchange!❄️☃️

🎁 Gifts should be under $10 or homemade

We’ll have hot chocolate and will also be drawing for our punch card winner! ☕️💝

🗓️ Monday, November 25th
⏰6-7pm
📍EUS Common Room

The POWEcast is back for Season 2! 🎙️

Tune in to this episode where we speak with our POWErful Engineer of the Month, Maya Dwivedi-Leng ✨ 

Maya is an M.Sc. student in Civil Engineering at McGill with a B.Eng. in Bioresource Engineering from McGill. She is currently  conducting her master’s thesis on wind farms in Ontario. Join us as Maya shares more about her education, her passion for renewable energy, and her experience as a woman in engineering! ♻️💕

🎧Link in bio to listen 
🔗 Link in bio to find out more about Maya’s initiatives

Join us next Monday for our sip and paint general meeting! 🎨

We will provide hot chocolate and mini paint canvases🖼️

It’s the perfect chance to unwind and get creative!👩🏽‍🎨

🗓️ Monday, November 18th 6-7pm
📍Engine
☕️Bring your own mug 

See you there ✨

Join us next Tuesday for our book club general meeting ✨📚

🗓️Tuesday, November 12th, 6-7pm
📍Engine

We will discuss an article or video sent previously in our general Slack channel and posted on our story! Then we’ll debrief by engaging in empowering conversations 💪

It’s not an actual book club but an opportunity to connect and contribute to conversation on uplifting women in our community! 🌟

We will have Krispy Kreme donuts available too! 🍩

Presenting our POWE execs and their coordinators! 🌟 

📸 - @mxrcuschong

Introducing the 7 incredible companies joining us for Speed Mentoring this Tuesday! 🌟

You will be able to engage directly with mentors from leading companies, gaining insights on professional development! 💡

Come prepared with questions to make the most of these conversations 🙋‍♀️

🗓️Tuesday, November 5th, 6-8pm
📍FDA 5&3, Engine
👔Business Casual

✨ POWE McGill Merch Sales are here! ✨

Our merch sales are open from November 1st to November 7th at midnight, so don’t miss your chance to grab some fun merch including our new sticker designs 👀! 

‼️To complete your order, be sure to fill out both the Google form and the Zeffy link. 

Link to both forms can be found in our linktree!
